data.title: Yuvika Chaudhary: Movies, Photos, Videos, News, Biography & Birthday
data.meta_description: Yuvika Chaudhary: Check out the list of all Yuvika Chaudhary movies along with photos, videos, biography and birthday. Also find latest Yuvika Chaudhary news on Times of India.
data.text:
Bigg Boss 9 couple Prince Narula and Yuvika Chaudhary announce pregnancy; former writes ‘Privika baby aane wala hai bahut jaldi’

etimes.in / Jun 25, 2024, 21:22 (IST)

Joyfully awaiting our first child's arrival, we express gratitude and excitement for the future. From the reality show to the grand wedding, our love story continues to flourish. Sharing our joy on social media with pictures of a car and toy baby car, symbolizing the anticipation of becoming parents.

Parents-to-be Prince Narula and Yuvika Chaudhary share an adorable video; write, “Happy pregnancy to us”

etimes.in / Jul 05, 2024, 09:27 (IST)

Prince Narula and Yuvika Chaudhary, known from Bigg Boss 9, share their pregnancy joy with fans. The couple's announcement was met with love from celebrities and fans alike. Their journey into parenthood is highly anticipated.

Exclusive: Splitsvilla X5’s Siwet Tomor on Prince Narula and Yuvika Chaudhary expecting a baby: I’m so excited and happy for them; we will celebrate soon

etimes.in / Jun 28, 2024, 08:45 (IST)

In my journey on Splitsvilla X5, emotions ran high after Siwet Tomar's eviction. Celebrating Prince Narula and Yuvika Chaudhary's pregnancy brought us joy. I am excited for the new member joining and look forward to the celebrations. The bond with Prince and Yuvika is special, and I can't wait to support them as they welcome their bundle of joy.

Are Prince Narula and Yuvika Chaudhary expecting their first baby? Here's what he shared in Bharti Singh's podcast

etimes.in / Apr 23, 2024, 13:55 (IST)

Prince Narula and Yuvika Chaudhary, expecting their first child, fell in love on Bigg Boss 9. They celebrated their marriage in 2018. Bharti Singh questioned Prince about their future child.

Gauahar Khan writes a heartfelt message for husband Zaid darbar, says 'We are graduating from the best universe called life'

etimes.in / Oct 05, 2023, 02:00 (IST)

Gauahar Khan frequently updates her Instagram with heartwarming photos featuring husband Zaid Darbar and their son, Zehaan. She recently expressed gratitude for their journey, receiving blessings and admiration from friends and fans for their love. Gauahar's stunning ethnic attire garnered praise, and she continues to connect with fans through social media.

Parmish Verma and Raftaar join hands for a new track

etimes.in / Sep 20, 2023, 23:12 (IST)

Punjabi singer-actor Parmish Verma has announced his collaboration with Raftaar for a new song. Parmish shared a picture on social media and mentioned that the song will be released later this year. This will be their second collaboration after the song 'Khulle Kharche.' Parmish Verma is also busy with his upcoming films 'Tabaah' and 'Rocky 3,' for which the release dates are yet to be announced.

Yuvika Chaudhary: Prince and I have been planning a child since we married, but it is in god’s hands

TNN / Jul 06, 2023, 08:11 (IST)

Actress Yuvika Chaudhary, who has been married to actor, singer and TV show host, Prince Narula for five years, says that the couple respects each other and gives each other enough space. She also says that while people persistently ask them about having a child, the couple has left that decision to god.

Yuvika Chaudhary plans a Valentine's Day surprise for hubby Prince Narula

TNN / Feb 14, 2023, 18:21 (IST)

Yuvika and Prince Narula are one of the cutest couples in the industry. Yuvika shared her valentine plans with us, here's what she did on the day.

Prince & I argue, our opinions differ, but in the end love completes us: Yuvika Chaudhary

Nov 11, 2022, 09:01 (IST)

For a couple that is looked up to as an ideal one, Yuvika Chaudhary says there’s a lot that goes on beyond the loved-up posts of husband Prince Narula and her.

Prince Narula, Yuvika Chaudhary roped in as hosts on 'Nach Baliye 10'

IANS / Aug 01, 2022, 18:02 (IST)

Celebrity couple Prince Narula and Yuvika Chaudhary, who won the title of reality TV show 'Nach Baliye 9' have been approached to host the upcoming season of 'Nach Baliye', though nothing has been confirmed officially.

Karan Kundrra, Prince Narula and others attend Munawar Faruqui’s comedy show in Mumbai

etimes.in / Jul 03, 2022, 19:42 (IST)

Lock Upp fame Munawar Faruqui’s career is skyrocketing ever since his Lock Upp season one win. The comedian has pleased fans with his skills several times thereafter.

Actress Yuvika Chaudhary adopts a new puppy; says “welcome home little one'

etimes.in / May 26, 2022, 20:31 (IST)

Bigg Boss fames Yuvika Chaudhary and husband Prince Narula welcomed a new puppy to their family. The couple had lost their dog, Buddy to a cardiac arrest earlier this month while Prince was away shooting for Lock Upp. The actress was very sad after the loss of her best friend

Exclusive - Prince Narula: My wife Yuvika and I've an amazing understanding and I knew Azma flirting with me would be harmless

etimes.in / May 08, 2022, 15:26 (IST)

In an exclusive interview with ETimes TV, Prince Narula opened up about his journey on the show, his bond with Munwar Faruqui and seeing his brother Karan Kundrra and Tejasswi together as Jailor and Warden on the show. He also spoke about Azma’s flirtatious behaviour towards him.

Yuvika Chaudhary lashes out at Karanvir Bohra for criticising her husband Prince Narula: "God bless him. I expected maturity from him"- Exclusive!

etimes.in / Apr 22, 2022, 22:44 (IST)

Yuvika Chaudhary is amused but not quite. Prince Narula has aggravated Karanvir Bohra in 'Lock Upp' and Bohra has been vocal about it. He has called Prince a Chachi who loves to gossip and said that he's disappointed that Prince supported Zeeshan Khan who according to him is a violent man.
